  "root_text": {
    "iti30:0.1": "Itivuttaka 30 ",
    "iti30:0.2": "Dukanipāta ",
    "iti30:0.3": "Paṭhamavagga ",
    "iti30:0.4": "Tapanīyasutta ",
    "iti30:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti30:2.1": "“Dveme, bhikkhave, dhammā tapanīyā. ",
    "iti30:2.2": "Katame dve? ",
    "iti30:2.3": "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco akatakalyāṇo hoti, akatakusalo, akatabhīruttāṇo, katapāpo, kataluddo, katakibbiso. ",
    "iti30:2.4": "So ‘akataṁ me kalyāṇan’tipi tappati, ‘kataṁ me pāpan’tipi tappati. ",
    "iti30:2.5": "Ime kho, bhikkhave, dve dhammā tapanīyā”ti. ",
    "iti30:2.6": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti30:2.7": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti30:3.1": "“Kāyaduccaritaṁ katvā, ",
    "iti30:3.2": "vacīduccaritāni ca; ",
    "iti30:3.3": "Manoduccaritaṁ katvā, ",
    "iti30:3.4": "yañcaññaṁ dosasañhitaṁ. ",
    "iti30:4.1": "Akatvā kusalaṁ kammaṁ, ",
    "iti30:4.2": "katvānākusalaṁ bahuṁ; ",
    "iti30:4.3": "Kāyassa bhedā duppañño, ",
    "iti30:4.4": "nirayaṁ sopapajjatī”ti. ",
    "iti30:5.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti30:5.2": "Tatiyaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti30:0.1": "So It Was Said 30 ",
    "iti30:0.2": "The Book of the Twos ",
    "iti30:0.3": "Chapter One ",
    "iti30:0.4": "Mortifying ",
    "iti30:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti30:2.1": "“These two things, mendicants, are mortifying. ",
    "iti30:2.2": "What two? ",
    "iti30:2.3": "It’s when someone hasn’t done good and skillful things that keep them safe, but has done bad things, violence and sin. ",
    "iti30:2.4": "Thinking, ‘I haven’t done good things’, they’re mortified. Thinking, ‘I have done bad things’, they’re mortified. ",
    "iti30:2.5": "These are the two things that are mortifying.” ",
    "iti30:2.6": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti30:2.7": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti30:3.1": "“Having done bad things ",
    "iti30:3.2": "by way of body, ",
    "iti30:3.3": "speech, and mind, ",
    "iti30:3.4": "and whatever else is corrupt; ",
    "iti30:4.1": "not having done good deeds, ",
    "iti30:4.2": "and having done many bad, ",
    "iti30:4.3": "when their body breaks up, that witless person ",
    "iti30:4.4": "is reborn in hell.” ",
    "iti30:5.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
